
- Arrays are passed as pointers in function.

  means function( int arr[] ) is same as function ( int *arr )



How to print size of array parameter in C++ ?


- can be passed as reference

  function( int (&arr)[10] )
            or
  function( int (&arr)[n] )


 --------------------------------------------------
 | size of array = sizeof(arr[]) / sizeof(arr[i]) |
 --------------------------------------------------
